{
  "stem": "8916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we went along with everybody else, just-- we received this-- this place, this housing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And huge numbers of people were just jammed into the area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the area of the ghetto was surrounded by brick walls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in a-- in an apartment house, with many apartments.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was several stories high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had one of the apartments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, of course, when more people moved in, we took in another couple, to share the apartment with us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't have any particular things that I-- that I-- that were exactly mine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we just took our stuff, our possessions, our furniture, our beds, and things that people own, and loaded it up in one of those wagons, horse-drawn wagons, and hauled it off into the-- into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not willingly, but there was no choice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If-- people who refused were, at worst, caught and brought to the ghetto, or shot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, uh huh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was basically just scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once something like that happens, the-- one's so shocked with the-- with this incident that it's hard to imagine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's a lot like being in a car accident, that-- that one gets spun around, and then-- and then just only later becomes scared and gets the shakes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a man who was, for some reason, escaping from a-- from a German officer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he just pulled out his gun and shot him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While we were in the ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- my friend and I went to take a-- a woman to the-- to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was a small woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was an older lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she needed to-- she was very ill.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
